Class NamedChannelsInput

Object
NamedChannelsInput
All Implemented Interfaces:
ProvidesStackInput, InputFromManager
Direct Known Subclasses:
NamedChannelsInputPart
public abstract class NamedChannelsInput
extends Object
implements ProvidesStackInput
Provides a set of channels as an input, each of which has a name. Only a single time-point is possible
